                  </span></div><br><div class="comment">
                  <span class="c00">&gt; not entirely clear on how crypto works<p>Sometimes they accidentally weaken the algorithm (like by chopping it&#x27;s key bits in half through a weak RNG). Crypto is hard, even when the scammer probably has a good grasp. Which is useful in this case.<span>
